## ‚úÖ **Fixed! Scroll Now Works on ALL Pages!**

**What I updated:**

**Before (only worked on homepage):**
```css
@media (max-height: 710px) {
    .home-menu,          ‚Üê Only homepage
    .side-panel nav {    ‚Üê Didn't target correctly
        overflow-y: auto;
        max-height: 100vh;
    }
}
```

**After (works everywhere):**
```css
@media (max-height: 710px) {
    .home-menu,          ‚Üê Homepage
    .side-menu,          ‚Üê All other pages  
    .side-panel nav,     ‚Üê Backup selector
    .side-panel {        ‚Üê Additional backup
        overflow-y: auto;
        max-height: 100vh;
    }
}
```

